{"tid":809281,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺出到嚟做嘢仲好似讀U咁Deadline先交嘢嘅人好不負責任？","createTime":"2018-09-07T04:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T16:38:39.000Z","uid":6122,"like":9,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"af0875d94f90a2a677b778459dbc5a9020757ba8","tid":809281,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"交低個Deadline其實係預你早兩三成時間就交<br />\n譬如俾兩星期你就應該早兩三日做好<br />\n方便其他同事做返checking同make amendment <br />\n但有啲人仲好似Deadline fighter最後一刻先做係十分自私<br />\n其他同事根本冇時間跟進<br />\n有時仲要成份大改<br />\n自私行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b318141a5d86f63924af46f2c10a1385d8ab13ff","tid":809281,"uid":189053,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5177845998dd5c0cb510bc0004e5da735eabf041","tid":809281,"uid":169048,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:11:39.000Z","msg":"咁撚早交 有得分咩"},{"pid":"79ac593261f07a2d6d42fef89c065bfbfd28dc6a","tid":809281,"uid":187072,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"想人早d做完咪set個deadline早d囉<br />\n定係你唔知deadline 點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c5654d45956efa3a5c4f49a182cd42e457bdf9","tid":809281,"uid":79245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:22:22.000Z","msg":"早交出多份糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   唔係咁我早交做咩"},{"pid":"16bf314528d0d4f26c55f15767f8e2ebbe1470a2","tid":809281,"uid":120123,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:27:44.000Z","msg":"屌你，咁你個deadline就set早d啦<br />\n真係set到最尾果日，第一日出來返工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593594b9f33f5a9191402299d9d7aaa6368e2444","tid":809281,"uid":109462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:35:56.000Z","msg":"長命功夫長命做，職場制度長期都係懲罰緊高效率嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為當你快手快腳做完嘢之後馬上就會有另一份新嘢做，但人工又唔係高過其他同事，咁做得快豈不是懲罰緊自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f413e979da85ab10051b4678ce02a57bf66fcd","tid":809281,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:42:37.000Z","msg":"早啲做完一係就比多啲野你做，一係就炒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非有得分，否則打工真係拖得就拖。<br />\n<br />\n試過做同一樣野<br />\n大家都有十日時間去做，<br />\n一個人用五日時間就做完，老闆覺得佢成日偷懶唔做野同做得唔好。<br />\n一個人用足十日拖慢去做，老闆反而係覺得佢勤力。<br />\n其實明明係五日果個做得好啲，因為佢有時間執返啲錯處，但奈何出黎做野就係咁。"},{"pid":"88db755a7f3d0bd58d85e385f13ed2b177691998","tid":809281,"uid":196321,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:46:05.000Z","msg":"老闆: 依你係DEADLINE前幾日做完?岩啦呢度有3份文件,幫我入埋機,聽朝要既"},{"pid":"b4a4a52abfe280919df172056a4c1d459ceb12b5","tid":809281,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">交低個Deadline其實係預你早兩三成時間就交</span><br />\n譬如俾兩星期你就應該早兩三日做好<br />\n方便其他同事做返checking同make amendment <br />\n但有啲人仲好似Deadline fighter最後一刻先做係十分自私<br />\n其他同事根本冇時間跟進<br />\n有時仲要成份大改<br />\n自私行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平行宇宙嚟嘅 assumption??? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c242479fb9aa4ec73845e2fd2fbd39342893a714","tid":809281,"uid":150510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"咁你咪set早個deadline2-3日囉On9"},{"pid":"e4de8730f14cba6bbe728dc5ac58fc95731db8bd","tid":809281,"uid":169487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"不留都過左deadline俾人追果時先話聽日交"},{"pid":"0a4c96274d1077e20c71d92ea19f620429e9c8eb","tid":809281,"uid":31705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"咁你不如下下都同人講 份野急要 即刻比你啦<br />\n你又要set deadline又要人估中你心思早d交 <br />\n咁大個人好心你咪咁無腦啦 仲響度扮